<h2><span class="t-type">TD</span> <span class="t-title">Acquisition - Interface Graphique </span><span class="t-year">(2&egrave;me ann&eacute;e)</span></h2>
<ul>
  <li>Impl&eacute;mentation en C++ d'un syst&egrave;me d'acquisistion d'images par cam&eacute;ra.</li>
  <li>Syst&egrave;me d'acquisition: Matrox Imaging Library (MIL); Frame grabber: Matrox Meteor II.</li>
  <li>Graphical User Interface: Borland C++ Builder 4 </li>
</ul>

