    <h2  ><span class="t-type">TP</span> <span class="t-title">Probabilit&eacute; et Statistique</span> <span class="t-year">(3&egrave;me ann&eacute;e)</span></h2>
    <ul>
	  <li>Lois de probabilit&eacute;s, variables et signaux al&eacute;atoires, r&eacute;gression lin&eacute;aire, estimation, test d'hypoth&egrave;ses (Matlab, Windows)
	  </li>
	  <li>Les donn&eacute;es:
              <ul>
                <li> L'echantillon: notes sur 20 mati&egrave;res pour 75 &eacute;tudiants: <a href="stat/download/notes">[txt/data]</a></li>
                  <li>Le test de diff&eacute;rences premi&egrave;res: <a href="stat/download/diffpre.m">[Matlab]</a></li>
                  <li> Le test Kolmogorov-Smirnov: <a href="stat/download/ks.m">[Matlab]</a></li>
              </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>

